Listen to this before you carry on reading: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=54l3lvChkqE&feature=youtu.be

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nSDgHBxUbVQ&list=PL2vrmw2gup2Jre1MK2FL72rQkzbQzFnFM&index=17

 

 

Insidia, the team that reached the finals with 5 default wins and one monument. Don't forget, we tried. The Dream. RIP it was so young. Proximity, Insidia, Allah for 5 minutes, a team of dreams, a family.

THE REAL CARRIER:

The big boi himself, LANCE!

 

It’s been a bumpy ride, Insidia a real family. Thank you for the great memories. Good bye..

 

RIP </3
